      "rendered": "Help Promote the 2021 Global NGO Technology Survey!"
    },
    "content": {
      "rendered": "<p>A country must have a minimum of 100 survey responses for the data to be made public. Email is the most effective way to promote the survey. If your organization sends an email to your list about the 2021 Global NGO Technology Survey, please <a href=\"http://www.nptechforgood.com/heather-mansfield/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><strong>contact Heather Mansfield</strong></a> to let her know and request that your country&#8217;s data be made public.</p>\n<p>The promo graphics and text below can be used to help promote the <a href=\"https://survey.alchemer.com/s3/6079524/2021-Global-NGO-Technology-Survey\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><strong>2021 Global NGO Technology Survey</strong></a> and the <a href=\"http://www.nptechforgood.com/open-data-project/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><strong>Open Data Project</strong></a>. You can also <a href=\"https://www.dropbox.com/sh/c3ouhyufykamtc6/AAAbxjJWrwMs7G5b2Pf9nFGxa?dl=0\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>download the promo graphics and text directly from Dropbox</strong></a>. Thank you!</p>\n<hr />\n<h2>2021 Global NGO Technology Survey Promo Graphics</h2>\n<h5 style=\"text-align: center;\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-28774 size-full\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/2021-Global-NGO-Technology-Survey-1200-x-300.png?resize=960%2C240\" alt=\"\" width=\"960\" height=\"240\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/2021-Global-NGO-Technology-Survey-1200-x-300.png?w=1200&amp;ssl=1 1200w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/2021-Global-NGO-Technology-Survey-1200-x-300.png?resize=300%2C75&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/2021-Global-NGO-Technology-Survey-1200-x-300.png?resize=1024%2C256&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/2021-Global-NGO-Technology-Survey-1200-x-300.png?resize=768%2C192&amp;ssl=1 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\" />\u25b2 Email Header Promo Graphic (1024 x 256)</h5>\n<h5 style=\"text-align: center;\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-28777 aligncenter\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/2021-Global-NGO-Technology-Survey-1200-x-1200.png?resize=960%2C480\" alt=\"\" width=\"960\" height=\"480\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/2021-Global-NGO-Technology-Survey-1200-x-1200.png?w=1200&amp;ssl=1 1200w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/2021-Global-NGO-Technology-Survey-1200-x-1200.png?resize=300%2C150&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/2021-Global-NGO-Technology-Survey-1200-x-1200.png?resize=1024%2C512&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/2021-Global-NGO-Technology-Survey-1200-x-1200.png?resize=768%2C384&amp;ssl=1 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\" />\u25b2 Social Media Promo Graphic #1 (1024 x 512)</h5>\n<h5 style=\"text-align: center;\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-28783 aligncenter\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/2021-Global-NGO-Technology-Survey-1200-x-1200-1.png?resize=960%2C960\" alt=\"\" width=\"960\" height=\"960\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/2021-Global-NGO-Technology-Survey-1200-x-1200-1.png?w=1200&amp;ssl=1 1200w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/2021-Global-NGO-Technology-Survey-1200-x-1200-1.png?resize=300%2C300&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/2021-Global-NGO-Technology-Survey-1200-x-1200-1.png?resize=1024%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/2021-Global-NGO-Technology-Survey-1200-x-1200-1.png?resize=150%2C150&amp;ssl=1 150w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/2021-Global-NGO-Technology-Survey-1200-x-1200-1.png?resize=768%2C768&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/2021-Global-NGO-Technology-Survey-1200-x-1200-1.png?resize=200%2C200&amp;ssl=1 200w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/2021-Global-NGO-Technology-Survey-1200-x-1200-1.png?resize=75%2C75&amp;ssl=1 75w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/2021-Global-NGO-Technology-Survey-1200-x-1200-1.png?resize=80%2C80&amp;ssl=1 80w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\" />\u25b2 Social Media Promo Graphic #2 (1024 x 1024)</h5>\n<h5 style=\"text-align: center;\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-28785 aligncenter\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/2021-Global-NGO-Technology-Survey-1200-x-600-2.png?resize=960%2C480\" alt=\"\" width=\"960\" height=\"480\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/2021-Global-NGO-Technology-Survey-1200-x-600-2.png?w=1200&amp;ssl=1 1200w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/2021-Global-NGO-Technology-Survey-1200-x-600-2.png?resize=300%2C150&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/2021-Global-NGO-Technology-Survey-1200-x-600-2.png?resize=1024%2C512&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/2021-Global-NGO-Technology-Survey-1200-x-600-2.png?resize=768%2C384&amp;ssl=1 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\" />\u25b2 Social Media Promo Graphic #3 (1024 x 512)</h5>\n<h5 style=\"text-align: center;\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-28787 aligncenter\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/2021-Global-NGO-Technology-Survey-1200-x-1200-2.png?resize=960%2C960\" alt=\"\" width=\"960\" height=\"960\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/2021-Global-NGO-Technology-Survey-1200-x-1200-2.png?w=1200&amp;ssl=1 1200w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/2021-Global-NGO-Technology-Survey-1200-x-1200-2.png?resize=300%2C300&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/2021-Global-NGO-Technology-Survey-1200-x-1200-2.png?resize=1024%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/2021-Global-NGO-Technology-Survey-1200-x-1200-2.png?resize=150%2C150&amp;ssl=1 150w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/2021-Global-NGO-Technology-Survey-1200-x-1200-2.png?resize=768%2C768&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/2021-Global-NGO-Technology-Survey-1200-x-1200-2.png?resize=200%2C200&amp;ssl=1 200w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/2021-Global-NGO-Technology-Survey-1200-x-1200-2.png?resize=75%2C75&amp;ssl=1 75w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/2021-Global-NGO-Technology-Survey-1200-x-1200-2.png?resize=80%2C80&amp;ssl=1 80w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\" />\u25b2 Social Media Social Media Promo Graphic #4 (1024 x 1024)</h5>\n<hr />\n<h2>2021 Global NGO Technology Survey Promo Text</h2>\n<p>The promo text below can be used to help promote the survey to your email list and social media communities, however using your own voice and tone will likely work best!</p>\n<h6><strong>Email:</strong></h6>\n<p>The <strong><a href=\"http://www.nptechforgood.com/open-data-project/\">2021 Open Data Project</a></strong> is based on the survey responses from the Global NGO Technology Survey. Published in multiple languages, the survey seeks to gain a better understanding of how NGOs, nonprofits, and charities worldwide use technology for digital marketing and fundraising. Survey questions cover website and email communications, online fundraising tools, social media, and productivity and security software.</p>\n<p>The <strong><a href=\"https://survey.alchemer.com/s3/6079524/2021-Global-NGO-Technology-Survey\">2021 Global NGO Technology Survey</a></strong> is 100% anonymous and once submitted, you will be provided instant access to the data which can be browsed online or downloaded into Excel, PowerPoint, a PDF, and/or Word. The anonymized survey data is available in real-time by region and country and as a global average.</p>\n<p>The more survey respondents we have, the better the data \u2013 so please volunteer 6-12 minutes of your time and take the survey!</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>[<a href=\"https://survey.alchemer.com/s3/6079524/2021-Global-NGO-Technology-Survey\">Take the Survey</a>]</strong></p>\n<h6><strong>Social Media:</strong></h6>\n<p>The 2021 Global NGO Technology Survey examines how charitable organizations worldwide use technology for digital marketing and fundraising. Take the survey and once submitted, you will be provided instant access to the survey data: <strong><a href=\"http://www.nptechforgood.com/open-data-project/\">http://www.nptechforgood.com/open-data-project</a></strong></p>\n<p>The 2021 Global NGO Technology Survey is 100% anonymous and once submitted, you can browse and download the data in real-time by region and country and as a global average. Please take the survey! <a href=\"http://www.nptechforgood.com/open-data-project\"><strong>http://www.nptechforgood.com/open-data-project</strong></a></p>\n<p>The 2021 Global NGO Technology Survey is available in English, French, and Spanish! Please volunteer 6-10 minutes of your time and take the survey: <a href=\"http://www.nptechforgood.com/open-data-project\"><strong>http://www.nptechforgood.com/open-data-project</strong></a></p>\n<p>Work at an NGO, nonprofit, or charity? Then please take the 2021 Global NGO Technology Survey: <a href=\"http://www.nptechforgood.com/open-data-project\"><strong>http://www.nptechforgood.com/open-data-project</strong></a></p>\n<p>The more survey responses we have, the better the data! Please volunteer 6-10 minutes of your time and take the 2021 Global NGO Technology Survey: <a href=\"http://www.nptechforgood.com/open-data-project\"><strong>http://www.nptechforgood.com/open-data-project</strong></a></p>\n<p>Work at an NGO, nonprofit, or charity? Then please take the 2019 Global NGO Technology Survey: <strong><a href=\"http://www.nptechforgood.com/open-data-project/\">http://www.nptechforgood.com/open-data-project</a></strong></p>\n<hr />\n<h2>2021 Open Data Project Graphics</h2>\n<h5 style=\"text-align: center;\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-28792 aligncenter\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Open-Data-Project-1200-x-300.png?resize=960%2C240\" alt=\"\" width=\"960\" height=\"240\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Open-Data-Project-1200-x-300.png?w=1200&amp;ssl=1 1200w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Open-Data-Project-1200-x-300.png?resize=300%2C75&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Open-Data-Project-1200-x-300.png?resize=1024%2C256&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Open-Data-Project-1200-x-300.png?resize=768%2C192&amp;ssl=1 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\" />\u25b2 Email Header Promo Graphic (1024 x 256)</h5>\n<h5 style=\"text-align: center;\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-28794 aligncenter\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Open-Data-Project-1200-x-600.png?resize=960%2C480\" alt=\"\" width=\"960\" height=\"480\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Open-Data-Project-1200-x-600.png?w=1200&amp;ssl=1 1200w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Open-Data-Project-1200-x-600.png?resize=300%2C150&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Open-Data-Project-1200-x-600.png?resize=1024%2C512&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Open-Data-Project-1200-x-600.png?resize=768%2C384&amp;ssl=1 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\" />\u25b2 Social Media Promo Graphic #1 (1024 x 512)</h5>\n<h5 style=\"text-align: center;\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-28795 aligncenter\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Open-Data-Project-1200-x-1200.png?resize=960%2C960\" alt=\"\" width=\"960\" height=\"960\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Open-Data-Project-1200-x-1200.png?w=1200&amp;ssl=1 1200w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Open-Data-Project-1200-x-1200.png?resize=300%2C300&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Open-Data-Project-1200-x-1200.png?resize=1024%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Open-Data-Project-1200-x-1200.png?resize=150%2C150&amp;ssl=1 150w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Open-Data-Project-1200-x-1200.png?resize=768%2C768&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Open-Data-Project-1200-x-1200.png?resize=200%2C200&amp;ssl=1 200w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Open-Data-Project-1200-x-1200.png?resize=75%2C75&amp;ssl=1 75w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Open-Data-Project-1200-x-1200.png?resize=80%2C80&amp;ssl=1 80w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\" />\u25b2 Social Media Promo Graphic #1 (1024 x 1024)</h5>\n<hr />\n<h2>2021 Open Data Promo Text</h2>\n<h5>Email:</h5>\n<p>The <strong><a href=\"http://www.nptechforgood.com/open-data-project/\">2021 Open Data Project</a></strong> is based on the survey responses from the Global NGO Technology Survey. Published in multiple languages, the survey seeks to gain a better understanding of how NGOs, nonprofits, and charities worldwide use technology for digital marketing and fundraising. Survey questions cover website and email communications, online fundraising tools, social media, and productivity and security software.</p>\n<p>The <strong><a href=\"https://survey.alchemer.com/s3/6079524/2021-Global-NGO-Technology-Survey\">2021 Global NGO Technology Survey</a></strong> is 100% anonymous and once submitted, you will be provided instant access to the data which can be browsed online or downloaded into Excel, PowerPoint, a PDF, and/or Word. The anonymized survey data is available in real-time by region and country and as a global average.</p>\n<p>The more survey respondents we have, the better the data \u2013 so please volunteer 6-12 minutes of your time and take the survey!</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>[<a href=\"https://survey.alchemer.com/s3/6079524/2021-Global-NGO-Technology-Survey\">Take the Survey</a>]</strong></p>\n<h5>Social Media:</h5>\n<p>The 2021 Open Data Project provides digital marketing and fundraising benchmarks for charitable organizations worldwide. Learn more. Take the survey. Access the data: <strong><a href=\"http://www.nptechforgood.com/open-data-project\">http://www.nptechforgood.com/open-data-project</a></strong></p>\n<p>The 2021 Open Data Project is based on the survey responses from the 2021 Global NGO Technology Survey. The anonymized survey data is available in real-time by region and country and as a global average. To begin, learn more and take the survey: <strong><a href=\"http://www.nptechforgood.com/open-data-project\">http://www.nptechforgood.com/open-data-project</a></strong></p>\n<p>Open data is the idea that some data should be freely available to everyone to use and\u00a0republish as they wish. For the NGO/NPO/charity sector, Nonprofit Tech for Good has launched the 2021 Open Data Project. Learn more and participate: <strong><a href=\"http://www.nptechforgood.com/open-data-project\">http://www.nptechforgood.com/open-data-project</a></strong></p>\n<hr />\n<p>To receive quarterly updates and analysis of the Global NGO Technology Survey data, please sign up for <a href=\"https://mailchi.mp/nptechforgood/news\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>Nonprofit Tech for Good\u2019s email newsletter</strong></a>.</p>\n<h2>Open Data Project Sponsors</h2>\n<div class=\"wptb-container-legacy\" data-table-id=\"28026\">\n    <table class=\"wptb-preview-table wptb-element-main-table_setting-28026\" data-reconstraction=\"1\" style=\"border-width: 0px; border-style: solid; border-image: initial;\" data-wptb-table-tds-sum-max-width=\"267\" data-wptb-cells-width-auto-count=\"1\" role=\"table\" data-table-columns=\"2\" data-wptb-header-background-color=\"\" data-wptb-even-row-background-color=\"\" data-wptb-odd-row-background-color=\"\" data-wptb-extra-styles=\"LyogRW50ZXIgeW91ciBjdXN0b20gQ1NTIHJ1bGVzIGhlcmUgKi8=\"><tbody><tr class=\"wptb-row\"><td class=\"wptb-cell\" style=\"border-width: 1px; width: 107px;\" data-x-index=\"0\" data-y-index=\"0\"><div class=\"wptb-image-container wptb-ph-element wptb-element-image-8 edit-active\" data-wptb-image-alignment=\"center\"><div class=\"wptb-image-wrapper\">            <a style=\"display: block;\" class=\"\" href=\"https://www.eventgroove.com/\" target=\"_blank\">                                <img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wptb-image-element-target\" height=\"44\" width=\"200\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Eventgroove-Logo.png?resize=200%2C44\" style=\"width: 100%;\">            </a>        </div></div></td><td class=\"wptb-cell\" style=\"border-width: 1px;\" data-x-index=\"1\" data-y-index=\"0\"><div class=\"wptb-text-container wptb-ph-element wptb-element-text-3\" style=\"color: rgb(61, 70, 69); font-size: 15px;\"><div class=\"\" style=\"position: relative;\"><p><strong><a data-mce-href=\"https://www.eventgroove.com/\" href=\"https://www.eventgroove.com/\" style=\"color: rgb(30, 75, 176);\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Eventgroove</a></strong>&nbsp;is a one-stop platform for virtual, hybrid, and in-person events that offers event management, online fundraising, ticketing, and online storefronts for print and digital merchandise.</p></div></div></td></tr><tr class=\"wptb-row\" data-wptb-bg-color=\"\"><td class=\"wptb-cell\" data-y-index=\"1\" data-x-index=\"0\" style=\"border-width: 1px; width: 107px;\"><div class=\"wptb-image-container wptb-ph-element wptb-element-image-7\"><div class=\"wptb-image-wrapper\">            <a style=\"display: block;\" href=\"https://funraise.org/funraise-free\" target=\"_blank\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/funraise-free.png?resize=200%2C88\" height=\"88\" width=\"200\" style=\"width: 100%;\"></a>        </div></div></td><td class=\"wptb-cell\" data-y-index=\"1\" data-x-index=\"1\" style=\"border-width: 1px;\" data-wptb-css-td-auto-width=\"true\"><div class=\"wptb-text-container wptb-ph-element wptb-element-text-1\" style=\"color: rgb(61, 70, 69); font-size: 15px;\"><div class=\"\" style=\"position: relative;\"><p><a data-mce-href=\"https://funraise.org/funraise-free\" href=\"https://funraise.org/funraise-free\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" style=\"color: rgb(30, 75, 176);\"><strong>Funraise</strong></a>&nbsp;combines every fundraising tool that nonprofits need for success\u2014in one easy-to-use platform. Get started with free fundraising tools. Upgrade as you grow.</p></div></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n</div>\n\n",
