    "excerpt": {
      "rendered": "<p>A country must have a minimum of 100 survey responses for the data to be made public. Email is the most effective way to promote the survey. If your organization sends an email to your list about the 2021 Global NGO Technology Survey, please contact Heather Mansfield to let her know and request that your country&#8217;s data be made public. The promo graphics and text below can be used to help promote the 2021 Global NGO Technology Survey and the Open Data Project. You can also download the promo graphics and text directly from Dropbox. Thank you! 2021 Global NGO </p>\n",
